    </p>
    <p>
      Clone Hero is a classic instrument based rhythm game for Windows, Mac,
      Linux, and Android. It's playable with any 5 or 6 fret guitar controller,
      any midi drum kit, any game controller and even your keyboard! Jam out with
      Drums, 5-fret Guitar, or 6-fret Guitar online or local!
